    "There is little excuse for a PM who does not carry out many back-tests, even if only to vary the parameters around their chosen values.",
    "Large problems.",
    "We now investigate the scaling of the method with problem size.",
    "As outlined in §3.3, a factor model improves the scaling from O(n 3) to O(nk 2).",
    "To illustrate this, we solve the Markowitz problem for different values of n and k using randomly generated but realistic data."
